[30;1m265 | [0m[35m## Why another project? Why not build on Docker-py?[0m
[30;1m266 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m80 | [0m[35mdo with the Docker daemon, a `client_config` attribute is there and must be passed around.[0m
[30;1m81 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m82 | [0m[35mThis `client_config` tells the Docker CLI how to connect to the daemon. [0m
[30;1m83 | [0m[35mYou can think of it of the collection of all the arguments that are at the start of the CLI.[0m
[30;1m84 | [0m[35mFor example `docker -H ssh://my_user@my_ip ...`.[0m
[30;1m85 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m86 | [0m[35mEach sub-component of the CLI is in a separate directory. [0m
